  "prompt": "What are best computer games?",
  "response": "The \"best\" computer games can be subjective and depend on personal preferences, but there are several titles that are widely regarded as exceptional due to their gameplay, storytelling, graphics, and overall impact on the gaming industry. Here\u2019s a list of some of the most acclaimed games across various genres:\n\n### **Action/Adventure**\n1. **The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild** (Nintendo Switch, but playable on PC via emulators)  \n2. **Red Dead Redemption 2**  \n3. **God of War** (2018)  \n4. **Horizon Zero Dawn**  \n5. **Assassin\u2019s Creed Odyssey/Valhalla**  \n\n### **Role-Playing Games (RPGs)**\n1. **The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt**  \n2. **Elden Ring**  \n3. **Dark Souls Series**  \n4. **Mass Effect Series**  \n5. **Divinity: Original Sin 2**  \n\n### **First-Person Shooters (FPS)**\n1. **Half-Life 2**  \n2. **DOOM (2016) / DOOM Eternal**  \n3. **Counter-Strike: Global Offensive**  \n4. **Overwatch**  \n5. **Call of Duty: Modern Warfare Series**  \n\n### **Strategy Games**\n1. **Civilization VI**  \n2. **StarCraft II**  \n3. **XCOM 2**  \n4. **Total War: Warhammer Series**  \n5. **Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition**  \n\n### **Multiplayer/Online Games**\n1. **Fortnite**  \n2. **League of Legends**  \n3. **Dota 2**  \n4. **Apex Legends**  \n5. **World of Warcraft**  \n\n### **Puzzle/Indie Games**\n1. **Portal 2**  \n2. **Celeste**  \n3. **Stardew Valley**  \n4. **Hollow Knight**  \n5. **Among Us**  \n\n### **Survival/Open World**\n1. **Minecraft**  \n2. **Subnautica**  \n3. **The Forest**  \n4. **Valheim**  \n5. **Rust**  \n\n### **Horror Games**\n1. **Resident Evil 2 (Remake)**  \n2. **Silent Hill 2**  \n3. **Dead Space**  \n4. **Outlast**  \n5. **Amnesia: The Dark Descent**  \n\n### **Simulation**\n1. **The Sims 4**  \n2. **Euro Truck Simulator 2**  \n3. **Cities: Skylines**  \n4. **Microsoft Flight Simulator**  \n5. **Stardew Valley** (also fits here)  \n\n### **Sports/Racing**\n1. **FIFA Series**  \n2. **Rocket League**  \n3. **Forza Horizon Series**  \n4. **Gran Turismo Series**  \n5. **Tony Hawk\u2019s Pro Skater 1+2**  \n\n### **Upcoming Games to Watch**\n1. **Starfield**  \n2. **The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom** (Switch/PC emulation)  \n3. **Baldur\u2019s Gate 3**  \n4. **Hogwarts Legacy**  \n5. **Dragon Age: Dreadwolf**  \n\nThese games are considered some of the best based on critical acclaim, player reviews, and cultural impact. What makes a game the \"best\" ultimately depends on your taste in genres, gameplay mechanics, and storytelling.",
